Normal flow: The user will select the truck off the map and be shown a pop-up 

interface giving information about that truck, its current location, and its future 

locations.

Alternate flow: The user will select the truck off a sortable list off the map. The 

same information about location will be available without using the map view.

Exceptions: The database fails to return information that we want to display, such as 

current position. 

